details.author: TTPlanetPig
details.title: Clothing Migration Kit
details.description: This is an experimental project focused on Stable Diffusion (SD) models. In a single generated image, the same object or character consistently maintains a very high level of consistency. I had already attempted to address this issue in the SDXL model.

details.author: pythongosssss
details.title: pythongosssss/ComfyUI-Custom-Scripts
details.description: This extension provides: Auto Arrange Graph, Workflow SVG, Favicon Status, Image Feed, Latent Upscale By, Lock Nodes & Groups, Lora Subfolders, Preset Text, Show Text, Touch Support, Link Render Mode, Locking, Node Finder, Quick Nodes, Show Image On Menu, Show Text, Workflow Managements, Custom Widget Default Values

details.author: TTPlanetPig
details.title: Comfyui_TTP_Toolset
details.description: This is a workflow for my simple logic amazing upscale node for DIT model. it can be common use for Flux,Hunyuan,SD3 It can simple tile the initial image into pieces and then use image-interrogator to get each tile prompts for more accurate upscale process. The condition will be properly handled and the hallucination will be significantly eliminated.
